<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٦٥ ... سُورَةُ الطَّلَاقِ ... آياتها ١٢ ... مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَطَلِّقُوهُنَّ لِعِدَّتِهِنَّ}</span> ... مُسْتَقْبِلَاتٍ لِعِدَّتِهِنَّ،<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> فِي طُهْرٍ لَمْ يَقَعْ فِيهِ جِمَاعٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَحْصُوا الْعِدَّةَ}</span> ... احْفَظُوهَا؛ لِتَعْلَمُوا وَقْتَ الرَّجْعَةِ إِنْ أَرَدْتُّمُ المُرَاجَعَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِفَاحِشَةٍ مُّبَيِّنَةٍ}</span> ... بِمَعْصِيَةٍ ظَاهِرَةٍ؛ كَالزِّنَى، وَالتَّطَاوُلِ عَلَى الزَّوْجِ بِاللِّسَانِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَلَغْنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ}</span> ... قَارَبْنَ أَنْ يَنْتَهِينَ مِنْ عِدَّتِهِنَّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَوَيْ عَدْلٍ}</span> ... صَاحِبَيْ عَدَالَةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَقِيمُوا}</span> ... أَدُّوا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَخْرَجًا}</span> ... فَرَجًا مِنْ كُلِّ ضِيقٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يَحْتَسِبُ}</span> ... لَا يَخْطُرُ بِبَالِهِ، وَلَا يَتَوَقَّعُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَسْبُهُ}</span> ... كَافِيهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَالِغُ أَمْرِهِ}</span> ... مُنَفِّذٌ حُكْمَهُ؛ لَا يَفُوتُهُ شَيْءٌ، وَلَا يُعْجِزُهُ مَطْلُوبٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَدْرًا}</span> ... أَجَلًا يَنْتَهِي إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَئِسْنَ}</span> ... انْقَطَعَ رَجَاؤُهُنَّ؛ لِكِبَرِهِنَّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ارْتَبْتُمْ}</span> ... شَكَكْتُمْ؛ فَلَمْ تَدْرُوا مَا الحُكْمُ فِيهِنَّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُوْلَاتُ الْأَحْمَالِ}</span> ... صَاحِبَاتُ الحَمْلِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِنْ حَيْثُ سَكَنتُم}</span> ... قِبَلَ سُكْنَاكُمْ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>